{"id":"extended-diagnostics/NG8104","title":"NG8104: Text attribute not binding\n\n無法繫結的文字屬性","contents":"<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/extended-diagnostics/NG8104.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng8104-text-attribute-not-binding無法繫結的文字屬性\">NG8104: Text attribute not binding\n\n無法繫結的文字屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8104#ng8104-text-attribute-not-binding無法繫結的文字屬性\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  <div class=\"diagnostic-description\">\n    <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"說明\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8104#說明\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8104#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">此診斷可確保將具有“特殊” Angular 繫結字首（ <code>attr.</code> 、 <code>style.</code> 和 <code>class.</code> ）的屬性解釋為繫結。例如，<code>&lt;div attr.id=\"my-id\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code> 不會將其解釋為繫結到 <code>id</code> 屬性，而只是當做一個常規屬性，並將按原樣出現在最終的 HTML 中（ <code>&lt;div attr.id=\"my-id\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code> ）。這可能不符合開發人員的意圖，其意圖可能是想將 <code>id</code> 設定為“my-id”（ <code>&lt;div id=\"my-id\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code> ）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This diagnostic ensures that attributes which have the \"special\" Angular binding prefix (<code>attr.</code>, <code>style.</code>, and\n<code>class.</code>) are interpreted as bindings. For example, <code>&lt;div attr.id=\"my-id\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code> will not\ninterpret this as an attribute binding to <code>id</code> but rather just a regular attribute and will appear\nas-is in the final HTML (<code>&lt;div attr.id=\"my-id\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>). This is likely not the intent of the developer.\nInstead, the intent is likely to have the <code>id</code> be set to 'my-id' (<code>&lt;div id=\"my-id\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>).</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-should-i-do-instead\" translation-result=\"on\">我該怎麼辦？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8104#what-should-i-do-instead\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">What should I do instead?<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8104#what-should-i-do-instead\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">當繫結到 <code>attr.</code>、<code>class.</code> 或 <code>style.</code> 時，請確保使用了 Angular 範本繫結語法。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When binding to <code>attr.</code>, <code>class.</code>, or <code>style.</code>, ensure you use the Angular template binding syntax.</p>\n\n<pre>  &lt;div [attr.id]=\"my-id\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div [style.color]=\"red\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div [class.blue]=\"true\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n</pre>\n<h2 id=\"what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\" translation-result=\"on\">如果我無法避免這種情況怎麼辦？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8104#what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">What if I can't avoid this?<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8104#what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">可以透過編輯專案的 <code>tsconfig.json</code> 檔案來禁用此診斷：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This diagnostic can be disabled by editing the project's <code>tsconfig.json</code> file:</p>\n\n<code-example format=\"json\" language=\"json\">\n\n{\n  \"angularCompilerOptions\": {\n    \"extendedDiagnostics\": {\n      \"checks\": {\n        \"textAttributeNotBinding\": \"suppress\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">有關更多資訊，請參閱<a href=\"extended-diagnostics#configuration\">擴充診斷配置</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">See <a href=\"extended-diagnostics#configuration\">extended diagnostic configuration</a> for more info.</p>\n\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics#configuration\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8104#description\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8104#ng8104-text-attribute-not-binding無法繫結的文字屬性\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8104#what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8104#what-should-i-do-instead\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8104#如果我無法避免這種情況怎麼辦\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8104#我該怎麼辦\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8104#說明\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/extended-diagnostics/NG8104.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}